data.description: Welcome Home! Assumable Loan!!! nestled on two large lots on a quiet cul-de-sac, boasts a spacious living area with custom built-in cabinetry for storage. The eat-in kitchen provides picturesque views of the expansive yard, complete with appliances & a roomy pantry. Conveniently adjacent, you'll find a laundry room and a single-car garage. The home features bedrooms with ample closet space and a full guest bathroom. The master bedroom offers a private bath adorned with modern tile and vanity. Outside, the fully fenced yard provides room for a fire pit, perfect for starlit evenings. A detached, air-conditioned workshop/studio caters to artists or fitness enthusiasts. This charming home is adorned with cool tones, shiplap accent walls and privacy. With a blend of modern amenities and farmhouse charm, this property beckons for exploration. Don't miss the opportunity to view this delightful home and versatile studio. The loan may be assumable so ask about the details!!
